! To make the icon appearing in the titlebar less blurry, (the mupdf
! icon in particular suffers from the issue,) it needs to be made
! slightly larger.  A border of the same color as the background is
! added in order to achieve this.  If not for the added border, the
! label background could actually be defined as parentrelative.
! Parentrelative means that the element inherits its colors from the
! textures behind it as is, in essence, completely transparent.
window.active.label.bg: flat border solid
window.active.label.bg.color: #3465a4
window.active.label.bg.colorTo: #407cca
window.active.label.bg.border.color: #3465a4
window.active.label.text.color: #ffffff

